                "invention-title": [
                    "Solid hydrogen storage power generation device",
                    "一种固体储氢发电装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a solid hydrogen storage power generation device which comprises a power generation device body, the power generation device body comprises an air exhaust mechanism, a fuel cell module and a hydrogen storage cylinder, the air exhaust mechanism, the fuel cell module and the hydrogen storage cylinder are installed in an outer shell, heat generated when the fuel cell module works is converted into hot air through the air exhaust mechanism, and the hot air is stored in the hydrogen storage cylinder; hot air enters the hydrogen storage cylinder, heat in the hot air enters the hydrogen storage cylinder to heat hydrogen in the hydrogen storage cylinder, the hydrogen can quickly enter the fuel cell module after absorbing the heat to provide hydrogen fuel for the fuel cell module, and the hot air is subsequently cooled into cold air and then blown to the fuel cell module; heat dissipation of the fuel cell can greatly improve efficiency when the temperature is high in summer, the service life of the fuel cell is prevented from being shortened, the situation that hydrogen cannot be discharged smoothly due to low temperature when the hydrogen storage cylinder outputs hydrogen in winter is avoided, heat can be recycled between the fuel cell module and the hydrogen storage cylinder, and the utilization efficiency of the solid hydrogen storage power generation device is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种固体储氢发电装置，包括：发电装置主体，该发电装置主体包括排风机构、燃料电池模块、储氢筒，将排风机构、燃料电池模块、储氢筒安装在外壳体内，通过排风机构将燃料电池模块工作时产生的热量形成热风，热风则进入到储氢筒内，热风内的热量则进入到储氢筒内，对储氢筒内的氢气进行加热，氢气则可以吸收热量后快速地进入到燃料电池模块内，为燃料电池模块提供氢气燃料，热风则后续温度降低成冷风，进而再吹到燃料电池模块上，夏天气温高燃料电池的散热会大大提供效率，避免减少燃料电池的使用寿命，冬天时储氢筒出氢时不会因温度低不能顺畅排出，燃料电池模块、储氢筒之间可以循环利用热量，提高了该固体储氢发电装置的利用效率。"
                }
            ]
